summary: an enb that makes skyrim feel harsh and cold
descriptionHtml:
[size=5]This is my new enb preset that is supposed to make skyrim feel more harsh and cold.

[/size]                                       [size=5]           [u]description

[/u][/size]this enb  is the exatct opposite of  my other enb, this enb makes feel more harsh and natural with decent fps drop.
i run this with a i7 4790k at 4.5 and a gtx 970 sc and i get a min of 55 fps.

I used amidean born textures, rw2, elfx,smim and , cot v, true storms and unbelievable grasses


                      [size=5]             installation

[/size]get enb serues 279, extract d3d9.dll and enbhost.
install preset.
in skyrim prefs ini put fgamma at 1.000
bfloatpointrendertartget=1
bTreesReceiveShadows=1bDrawLandShadows=1
